title: More whales stranded on remote New Zealand beach
text: More whales stranded on remote New Zealand beach A new pod of 240 whales swam aground at a remote New Zealand beach on Saturday just hours after weary volunteers managed to refloat a different group of whales following an earlier mass stranding.
